  "detailed_description": "               <strong>Neutrino</strong> is a minimalist pong-like game with <strong>very simple mechanics</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2100840/extras/34860087c93d5d9755ab37f2222e956d.poster.avif?t=1731072595\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2100840/extras/34860087c93d5d9755ab37f2222e956d.webm?t=1731072595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2100840/extras/34860087c93d5d9755ab37f2222e956d.mp4?t=1731072595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You <strong>rotate</strong> the aim, click to <strong>launch</strong> and if you are fast enough to change your mind, <strong>reset back</strong> try it again!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2100840/extras/1351de7dbd8f58c31e1ec84611ae08fb.poster.avif?t=1731072595\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2100840/extras/1351de7dbd8f58c31e1ec84611ae08fb.webm?t=1731072595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2100840/extras/1351de7dbd8f58c31e1ec84611ae08fb.mp4?t=1731072595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>                    <strong>13 levels</strong>, each with 10 different rooms - total to <strong>130 puzzles</strong>!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2100840/extras/9a95ce002280e33959f55d563012283d.poster.avif?t=1731072595\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2100840/extras/9a95ce002280e33959f55d563012283d.webm?t=1731072595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2100840/extras/9a95ce002280e33959f55d563012283d.mp4?t=1731072595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Difficulty evolves and new types of challenges are introduced gradually as you evolve further in the game, and if you're good enough o win level 12, you get the final boss to face to and finally escape the black hole!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controls</h2><br>You can use Mouse, Keyboard in 2 ways and PS4 Dual Shock, as you wish.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2100840/extras/f872852825ebb39ed7a9e188e11162f1.poster.avif?t=1731072595\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2100840/extras/f872852825ebb39ed7a9e188e11162f1.webm?t=1731072595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Thank you for playing Neutrino!</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2100840/extras/ad1683de827268ad56b96404911d82e2.poster.avif?t=1731072595\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2100840/extras/ad1683de827268ad56b96404911d82e2.webm?t=1731072595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2100840/extras/ad1683de827268ad56b96404911d82e2.mp4?t=1731072595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
